description: Product Description Duzzit Antibacterial Wipes are safe for use on most hard surfaces, in the kitchen, bathroom and nursery. Wipe clean door and appliance handles, taps, food preparation areas and floors . Kills 99.9 Percentof bacteria and viruses in a handy resealable pack, making these wipes quick and easy to use. Securely re-seal pack between uses to prevent the wipes drying from out. After use dispose of the wipe in household bin. Each pack contains 50 wipes Ingredients Active Ingredient: Benzalkonium Chloride (0.15% w/w). Contains amongst other ingredients: <5% Non Ionic Surfacants, EDTA, Parfum, Limonene, Methylisothiazolinone, Benzisothiazolinone, Disinfectants Safety Warning Cautionary notes: harmful to aquatic life with long lasting effects. Keep out of reach of children. Wash hands thoroughly after handling. Avoid release to the environment. Dispose of contents/container in accordance with local authority regulations. Use biocides safely. Always read the label and product information before use. See more
